The paper also mentions the efficient encoding and decoding algorithms for these codes, which could fall under the categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper may be relevant to the sub-categories of social and information networks (cs.SI) and computational complexity (cs.CC) due to the potential applications of mds codes in these areas.
